Useful for GMs

All Perceptions

Desicription:
Currently filled with the perception of all of the players, replace with the names of your players


all-perceptions

/w gm &{template:default} {{name=Perceptions}}  {{Hedros = DC [[@{Hedros|perception} + 10]] Roll [[1d20 +@{Hedros|perception}]] }} {{Brenioron = DC [[@{Brenioron |perception} + 10]] Roll [[1d20 +@{Brenioron |perception}]] }}{{Hops= DC [[@{Hops|perception} + 10]] Roll [[1d20 +@{Hops|perception}]] }} {{Vynce Galtstrad= DC [[@{Vynce Galtstrad|perception} + 10]] Roll [[1d20 +@{Vynce Galtstrad|perception}]] }}


Selected Defenses

Description:
Gm whisper the defense stats of the selected token

/w gm &{template:default} {{name=@{selected|character_name}'s Spell Book }} {{Armor=AC:@{selected|ac} Shield:@{selected|armor_class_shield}}} {{Saves=[Fort +@{selected|saving_throws_fortitude}](~selected|FORT) [Reflex+@{selected|saving_throws_reflex}](~selected|REF) [Will+@{selected|saving_throws_will}](~selected|WILL)}}



GM Initiative

Description:
Roll the initiative of the selected token and gm whisper the roll

gm-initiative

/w gm %{selected|Initiative}